    <item>
      <title>美联储的哈马克说市场很紧张，但运转</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/fed-s-hammack-says-markets-are-strained-but-functioning</link>
      <description><![CDATA[克利夫兰联邦储备银行总统贝丝·哈马克（Beth Hammack）表示，尽管最近唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的贸易政策引发的国债波动率最近发生了波动，但美国金融市场的运作良好。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/fed-s-hammack-says-markets-are-strained-but-functioning</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 20:54:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TPW的Pelosky警告我们对我们的资本遣返</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-09/tpw-s-pelosky-sees-capital-repatriation-out-of-us-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[TPW投资管理CIO Jay Pelosky在“彭博社结束”上说：“我们正处于远离美国股票的世俗变革中。” （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-09/tpw-s-pelosky-sees-capital-repatriation-out-of-us-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 20:40:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当特朗普对关税时，市场从恐惧转变为欣快感</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/markets-turn-from-fear-to-euphoria-as-trump-backpedals-on-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的美国与世界贸易战（Word Wor War）陷入困境后的五天，全球股票和债券市场陷入了混乱，他退缩了，在此过程中，他将金融体系从边缘退回。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/markets-turn-from-fear-to-euphoria-as-trump-backpedals-on-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 20:25:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贸易商陶醉于集会，想知道它可以走多远</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/traders-reveling-in-rally-wonder-just-how-far-it-can-go</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街穿越的反应迅速而欣喜。唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统暂停了一些最严厉的关税实施后，股票在几分钟内增加了3万亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/traders-reveling-in-rally-wonder-just-how-far-it-can-go</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 18:32:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Carney发誓要加快允许，使加拿大能源超级大国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/carney-pledges-to-speed-permits-make-canada-energy-superpower</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）承诺通过一项计划将加拿大成为全球“领先的能源超级大国”，该计划包括建立一个将在两年内决定重大项目的单一办事处。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/carney-pledges-to-speed-permits-make-canada-energy-superpower</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 18:09:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的关税暂停震动在“无赢”国库市场中产生</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/short-term-treasuries-plunge-as-trump-pauses-most-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统在周三将债券市场称为“美丽”。对于美国政府债务的交易者来说，这一天意味着纯混乱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/short-term-treasuries-plunge-as-trump-pauses-most-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 17:59:01 GMT</pubDate>
